{"tid":1909179,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「你知道黑警如何隨街綁架嗎？」TX2475，TY3572","createTime":"2020-03-03T19:31:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T22:09:28.000Z","uid":272569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f0454995940ce07c22ff64bddc15cc788ae65074","tid":1909179,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T19:31:16.000Z","msg":"「你知道黑警如何隨街綁架嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n此影片於2月19日22時45分將軍澳單車館外（即寶康路）錄得，片段內容為黑警私家車（車牌：TX2475，TY3572）突然於路上剎停，然後一眾便衣警落車隨即綁架一名男子上車。<br />\n<br />\n兩架便衣狗車（TX2475，TY3572）<br />\n早於12月由將軍澳烽火台channel證實為警方私家車，經常停泊喺將軍澳警署內。<br />\n<br />\n此段影片為香港警察有於路上隨街綁架之鐵證，亦可解釋為何有手足突然「被失蹤」及「被自殺」之情況<br />\n<br />\n#綁匪 <br />\n#被失蹤 <br />\n#被自殺<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkmissing/permalink/545505556094859/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkmissing%2Fpermalink%2F545505556094859%2F&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIW5pKsuoI6OgBDFn4N8w%2Bso%3D&h=577cbc13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkmissing/permalink/545505556094859/</a>"},{"pid":"a0b54e86d9f6e0df43b95da5bfdaccc3e2651e2a","tid":1909179,"uid":289782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T22:09:28.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}